OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FAn application calling for a new
OL,8,Finquest into the Summerland fire has
OL,9,Fbeen submitted to the Isle of Man's
OL,10,FAttorney General.
OL,12,FMembers of the 'Justice for
OL,13,FSummerland' campaign described the
OL,14,Fmove as a 'momentous day', adding that
OL,15,F'it is time to do the right thing and
OL,16,Fgrant us this inquest'.
OL,18,FThe Summerland fire remains the Isle
OL,19,Fof Man's greatest tragedy, killing 50
OL,20,Fpeople in a fire within a leisure
OL,21,Fcomplex in 1973.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/19
