OL,7,FThose who died in the fire were given
OL,8,Fa verdict of 'misadventure' after the
OL,9,Foriginal inquest, which the campaign
OL,10,Fis hoping to overturn.
OL,12,FSummerland survivor, Jackie Hallam,
OL,13,Fwas just 13 years old when she was
OL,14,Fcaught in the fire.
OL,16,FShe lost her mum Lorna Norton and best
OL,17,Ffriend Jane Tallon to the blaze.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
