OL,3,CFresh Summerland inquest application
OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FReferring to the application being
OL,8,Fsubmitted, she said: "It's just so
OL,9,Fimportant. It's important for us
OL,10,Fpersonally, but it's also important
OL,11,Ffor the future of justice.
OL,13,F"It's hugely important to me
OL,14,Fpersonally, but the two people that. I
OL,15,Flost were two out of fifty people.
OL,16,FFifty people were given a wrong
OL,17,Fverdict of misadventure, it was batted
OL,18,Fback to them as their own fault for
OL,19,Fentering a building - the building was
OL,20,Funsafe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
