OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,F"We deserve a proper inquest to look
OL,8,Fat all the evidence."
OL,10,FThe application for a fresh inquest
OL,11,Fwas submitted by Darragh Mackin, on
OL,12,Fbehalf of Phoenix Law - the law firm
OL,13,Frepresenting the campaign.
OL,15,FWithin the 389-page document is a
OL,16,Fcollection of reasons why the campaign
OL,17,Fbelieves a fresh inquest is necessary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
