OL,7,FWhen asked about the original
OL,8,Finvestigation, Darragh said: "The
OL,9,Finitial investigation appears to be
OL,10,Fsub-standard even by the standards of
OL,11,Fthe time, it seems to fall well below
OL,12,Fwhat is required.
OL,14,F"The conclusions and the evidence that
OL,15,Fwas ultimately considered seems to be
OL,16,Fminimal in the contrast to the vast
OL,17,Fswathes of evidence that the
OL,18,FCommission had in its possession."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
