OL,3,CFresh Summerland inquest application
OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FDr Frank Skuse was a forensic
OL,8,Fscientist, brought in to investigate
OL,9,Fthe smouldering leisure complex by the
OL,10,FUK Home Office, in the days following
OL,11,Fthe fire.
OL,13,FDarragh believes new evidence since
OL,14,F1973 surrounding Dr Skuse, could be
OL,15,Fthe key to a new inquest.
OL,17,FHe said: "He's the very same person
OL,18,Fwho led the various forensic
OL,19,Finvestigations into the Birmingham Six
OL,20,Fand the Judith Ward case. That stark
OL,21,Ffact needs to be investigated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
