OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,F"As we know, they were miscarriages of
OL,8,Fjustice, premised exclusively upon the
OL,9,Fforensic evidence in question, and for
OL,10,Fthose reasons we say that it would be
OL,11,Fa miscarriage of justice to allow
OL,12,Fanybody to stand over the original
OL,13,Fverdict of the Summerland tragedy."
OL,15,FThe 'Birmingham Six' were six men from
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland who were wrongfully
OL,17,Fsentenced to life in prison, following
OL,18,Ffalse convictions for the 1974
OL,19,FBirmingham pub bombings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
