OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FTheir convictions were eventually
OL,8,Fquashed by the Court of Appeal in 1991.
OL,10,FJudith Ward was another victim of a
OL,11,Fwrongful conviction, this one in
OL,12,Frelation to the M62 coach bombing in
OL,13,F1974.
OL,15,FA total of 12 people were killed after
OL,16,Fan IRA bomb exploded from within the
OL,17,Fluggage locker of the coach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/19
