OL,3,CFresh Summerland inquest application
OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FWard served over 17 years in prison,
OL,8,Fbefore her conviction was quashed,
OL,9,Fafter discovering forensic scientists
OL,10,Fhad withheld information in 1974,
OL,11,Fwhich strongly indicated her innocence.
OL,13,FIt was partly Dr Skuse's conclusions
OL,14,Fin both the Judith Ward case, and the
OL,15,FBirmingham Six, that contributed to
OL,16,Funjust convictions - and his flawed
OL,17,Fevidence presented in both cases were
OL,18,Feventually discredited.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
