OL,7,FDarragh said: "We must learn lessons
OL,8,Ffrom those cases, and the one lesson
OL,9,Fthat emanates from those cases is that
OL,10,Ftoo much time passed from their
OL,11,Fwrongful convictions, to the
OL,12,Foverturning and quashing of their
OL,13,Fconvictions and the righting the
OL,14,Fwrongs of those miscarriages of
OL,15,Fjustice."
OL,17,FThe application for a fresh inquest
OL,18,Falso contains a number of fire experts
OL,19,Fwho support the calls for a fresh
OL,20,Finquest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
