OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FThese include Professor Jose Torero, a
OL,8,Fleading expert in fire safety who has
OL,9,Fbeen involved in a number of fire
OL,10,Finvestigations, including the collapse
OL,11,Fof the World Trade Centre.
OL,13,FWriting within the application he
OL,14,Fsaid: 'There is no doubt in my mind
OL,15,Fthat the Summerland Fire Disaster is
OL,16,Fworthy of a new analysis conducted by
OL,17,Fpractitioners well versed in modern
OL,18,Ffire science and fire engineering
OL,19,Ftechniques.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
