OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FHe said: 'A full review of the
OL,8,Fstatements and reports that were
OL,9,Fgenerated by the original
OL,10,Finvestigations, in conjunction with
OL,11,Fthe post mortem reports, would assist
OL,12,Fnot only any future inquests relating
OL,13,Fto the Summerland disaster, but also
OL,14,Faid the families and friends of the
OL,15,Fvictims in better understanding how it
OL,16,Fwas that their loved ones came to lose
OL,17,Ftheir lives.'
OL,19,FThe original Summerland inquest was
OL,20,Fopened on 9 August 1973, a week after
OL,21,Fthe disaster took place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
