OL,7,FIt was then adjourned on 27 August
OL,8,F1974 to allow for the conclusion of
OL,9,Fthe Summerland Commission, which
OL,10,Fconcluded after 49 days of evidence.
OL,12,FThe inquest then concluded in a single
OL,13,Fday, where all reported deaths
OL,14,Freturned as 'death by misadventure'.
OL,16,FA fresh inquest may be considered if
OL,17,Fthe Attorney General sees it as
OL,18,F'desirable', as referenced in Section
OL,19,F6 of the Isle of Man Coroner of
OL,20,FInquest Act 1987.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
