OL,3,CFresh Summerland inquest application
OL,4,Csubmitted by survivors calling for
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FDarragh said: "We say not only does
OL,8,Fthe fresh evidence make the inquest
OL,9,Fdesirable, but when we have a tragedy
OL,10,Fof this size and scale, and we
OL,11,Fcontinue to have rumour and suspicion,
OL,12,Fthere needs to be an inquest."
OL,14,FBefore the application was submitted,
OL,15,Fthe Chief Minister of the Isle of Man
OL,16,Fwas directly questioned in parliament
OL,17,Fon whether the government would
OL,18,Fsupport a new inquest into Summerland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/19
