OL,7,FWhile he said it was 'not for me to
OL,8,Fmake judgement on what happened in
OL,9,FSummerland', he did confirm that the
OL,10,FAttorney General would 'give full
OL,11,Fconsideration' to any application
OL,12,Freceived.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Isle of Man
OL,15,FGovernment confirmed the application
OL,16,Fhas been received, adding that 'it
OL,17,Fwill be given appropriate
OL,18,Fconsideration'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/19
